And he waited for me that early?

48
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,840
He's so free.

49
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,160
I think he doesn't have any friends.

50
00:03:29,239 --> 00:03:33,280
Chairman Wei, these are the details
of students who got the scholarship.

51
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:36,440
Chairman Wei,
why are you interested in this?

52
