to the center for five years.

582
00:32:53,679 --> 00:32:55,000
What are his motives?

583
00:32:55,159 --> 00:32:58,039
That doesn't matter. At least
he's doing a good deed.

584
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:00,439
Fine. I understand now.

585
00:33:00,559 --> 00:33:04,439
I'm the only layman around.

586
00:33:06,319 --> 00:33:10,079
Tell me. Why did I try to woo him?

587
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:13,199
Actually, Xiao Fei is a nice person.

588
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,120
He's honest and attentive.

589
00:33:15,279 --> 00:33:17,640
Since he can donate all his money,

590
00:33:17,840 --> 00:33:20,600
I'm sure he can earn them back.

591
00:33:20,959 --> 00:33:23,279
Are you giving up already?

592
00:33:24,159 --> 00:33:25,120
No.

593
00:33:25,520 --> 00:33:28,279
Only Zhou Shi can handle him.

594
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,959
I think he doesn't like me.

595
00:33:30,120 --> 00:33:31,720
I don't need to waste my effort on him.

596
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:35,120
Besides, I have
some serious things to do.

597
00:33:36,319 --> 00:33:37,439
Serious things?

598
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:39,600
Are you sure about that?

599
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:42,400
Can't I just be serious for once?

600
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:45,360
I'll be going for an interview.
I'll work as a model.

601
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,640
Are you serious?

602
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:49,600
You need to be optimistic for that.

603
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:51,400
It doesn't suit you.

604
00:33:54,159 --> 00:33:57,319
Where can I get the money then?

605
00:33:57,480 --> 00:34:00,279
Shall I just wait for the money to come?

606
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:02,799
Listen. When I went for the interview,

607
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:08,079
the producer of the magazine
was the golden retriever among them.

608
00:34:08,279 --> 00:34:10,559
I mean golden bachelor.

609
00:34:10,999 --> 00:34:12,400
Even if I can't be his girlfriend,

610
00:34:12,559 --> 00:34:15,600
at least I'll be able
to meet some new friends.

611
00:34:16,519 --> 00:34:20,719
Besides, my next boyfriend must
be better than Gao Yang.

612
00:34:21,519 --> 00:34:24,079
I understand it now.

613
00:34:25,479 --> 00:34:26,479
Wait.

614
00:34:33,120 --> 00:34:34,279
Which one looks better?

615
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,840
