616
00:34:36,239 --> 00:34:38,719
They're counterfeits.
They look the same.

617
00:34:40,479 --> 00:34:42,759
Can you tell me that in a nicer way?

618
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:44,559
I wanted to have the real deal too.

619
00:34:44,759 --> 00:34:46,200
I sold them last month.

620
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,719
It's because I'm poor.

621
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:49,360
I wanted to use the real deal too.

622
00:34:50,719 --> 00:34:52,319
Okay. You can choose them yourself.

623
00:34:52,479 --> 00:34:54,479
-I'm going to play chess with Bai.
-Wait.

624
00:34:55,079 --> 00:34:56,440
Who's Bai?

625
00:34:57,559 --> 00:34:59,200
He's my friend in QQ.

626
00:34:59,319 --> 00:35:00,479
He uses the white pieces.

627
00:35:02,519 --> 00:35:04,120
You have a nickname for him?

628
00:35:04,319 --> 00:35:06,239
Fine. I'll not interrupt your date.

629
00:35:06,239 --> 00:35:07,120
Go now.

630
00:35:10,759 --> 00:35:11,999
Enjoy.

631
00:35:15,319 --> 00:35:17,799
Should I use this one?

632
