670
00:37:31,759 --> 00:37:33,559
Never mind then.
I won't wear this anymore.

671
00:37:33,719 --> 00:37:35,200
If something happened,

672
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,600
I would cause you trouble.

673
00:37:36,600 --> 00:37:38,880
Never mind that. Just take it.

674
00:37:39,319 --> 00:37:41,640
I don't have the money
for it's maintainence anyway.

675
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:43,759
If it can help you with your interview,

676
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:45,640
Wei Qing would be doing a good deed.

677
00:37:46,999 --> 00:37:49,559
Thanks then. I'll treat you next time.

678
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,519
Go now.

679
00:37:51,519 --> 00:37:52,479
I'll get ready now.

680
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:53,640
-Goodbye.
-Goodbye.

681
