688
00:38:28,519 --> 00:38:31,600
That day, you were nervous
when you were taking the call.

689
00:38:31,799 --> 00:38:33,120
I figured you would need some money.

690
00:38:33,239 --> 00:38:35,239
That's why I put the money in there.

691
00:38:36,160 --> 00:38:37,120
