692
00:38:38,680 --> 00:38:40,479
I can't tell you everything.

693
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:42,759
But I did use your money.

694
00:38:43,239 --> 00:38:45,360
Although this is not convincing,

695
00:38:45,559 --> 00:38:47,120
I'll repay the money later.

696
00:38:47,319 --> 00:38:48,200
Repay them?

697
00:38:50,239 --> 00:38:51,479
With what?

698
00:38:55,799 --> 00:38:58,719
Although I'm not sure
what you did with the money,

699
00:38:58,920 --> 00:39:03,519
you look like you're short on cash
since the first day I've met you.

700
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:06,680
And I'm rich.

701
00:39:07,600 --> 00:39:09,160
Why don't we make a deal then?

702
00:39:09,479 --> 00:39:10,239
What deal?

703
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,680
Be my girlfriend.

704
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:16,440
Besides being by my side all the time,

705
00:39:16,680 --> 00:39:19,719
