of a girlfriend as well.

706
00:39:20,319 --> 00:39:22,120
Of course. When I don't need you,

707
00:39:22,279 --> 00:39:24,279
you can do your own stuff.

708
00:39:24,479 --> 00:39:25,920
But when I need you,

709
00:39:26,079 --> 00:39:28,400
you need to appear immediately
and complete your duties.

710
00:39:28,719 --> 00:39:30,519
This won't last for too long.

711
00:39:30,719 --> 00:39:32,200
As long as you fulfill my requests,

712
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:33,840
