00:40:21,160 --> 00:40:22,440
Let me tell you a story.

732
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:23,759
In the past,

733
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:27,600
your senior, the ex-girlfriend of
Wei Qing, said the same thing.

734
00:40:27,759 --> 00:40:29,400
But after she became
Wei Qing's girlfriend,

735
00:40:29,559 --> 00:40:31,519
