And I do owe you some money.

755
00:41:11,799 --> 00:41:13,479
I don't know when I can
repay all of my debts.

756
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:16,160
But do you think you can
make me submit to you?

757
00:41:16,279 --> 00:41:18,160
